{"tid":819243,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機解唔到鎖，求教","createTime":"2018-09-14T15:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T10:01:25.000Z","uid":74090,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ab97b57afac84b53ea2d95c0074362ae3f4e19e0","tid":819243,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"屋企人部機平時用開4位密碼解鎖，無啦啦變左語音解鎖，㩒乜制都無反應開唔到，點<br />\n可以開番個Keyboard出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nReboot過都唔得<br />\n（麻煩唔好叫我俾番部機人，我有密碼，只係部機唔show Keyboard,不停叫我用語音解鎖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/235307_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F235307_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=84c33d3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90e4f39d9bd9e1d15f934164c15f58fd3dbeb89b","tid":819243,"uid":48286,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"android唔使畀番人啦，直接丟去垃圾桶， 人哋都係唔想要先丟出街"},{"pid":"ab8d2dd58a0b24236f93b0a3c9544e2b111d347e","tid":819243,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0119affbcb26fe1d7f21ecfefd889ca0d47a7d0c","tid":819243,"uid":74090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab8d2dd58a0b24236f93b0a3c9544e2b111d347e","tid":819243,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哇～你好幽默"},{"pid":"fcb3224cc749de0e57708338b6b48fb743ce6fdc","tid":819243,"uid":51039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"讀密碼唔得咩"},{"pid":"d4a66a7e9b49cea21add6aed3d3dd5b3fe3c47e9","tid":819243,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco